title: Woodworkers Journal Magazine. December 2010.
description:
Woodworkers Journal Magazine. December 2010.

Woodworker's Journal is designed for all woodworkers 
(from hobbyists to professionals) looking for new 
project ideas, woodworking techniques and shop jigs 
and tips that will enhance their time in the shop. 
Projects are presented in a detailed step-by-step 
format with photos and illustrations. A full size 
pattern is inserted in the middle of each issue. 
Departments cover joinery, finishing, products, 
techniques and hardware. 

Enjoy.
